{"tid":1112971,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃心穎講野嘅發音問題","createTime":"2019-04-17T16:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T06:21:31.000Z","uid":223006,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e7367168754516aa53a7e8f5f9b338c1e0a8f0c2","tid":1112971,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T16:47:05.000Z","msg":"呢兩句好多人討論佢有冇波、係咪臭雞格...<br />\n但其實都忽略左隻賓賓嘅廣東話發音問題, which係好撚un耳嘅!!<br />\n<br />\n佢係會將所有廣東話聲母係 J開頭嘅音, 誇大個J音起碼3倍...就咁講可能比較難明, 拎愛回家首歌舉個簡單例子大家就明:<br />\n<br />\n糖和鹽要怎麼比重 人氣新貨先<span style=\"color: red;\">進</span> 偏你<span style=\"color: red;\">鍾</span>愛舊古董<br />\n紅和藍也可相交碰 像我跟你吵架 生氣不過十分<span style=\"color: red;\">鐘</span><br />\n<br />\n也許所想所需<span style=\"color: red;\">總</span>有某些不會同 其實都可找到一扇門開通<br />\n<br />\n一雙手<span style=\"color: red;\">張</span>開可抱擁 一雙肩總不會超重 我與你結伴最大<span style=\"color: red;\">障</span>礙也被暖流解凍<br />\n手牽手身心都放鬆 小種子親手每天<span style=\"color: red;\">栽種</span> 同笑著喊著我若有夢你定起哄 一起飛<span style=\"color: red;\">縱</span><br />\n<br />\n老實講..其實真係好撚un耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b714e01b51eb6b3ec64591f8a754869e284e2ff6","tid":1112971,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e030416c2a7f8b0057a9fb5d86de7a299ae73c8","tid":1112971,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e7422e7cdd964bcc30f0147ed3648273ecfb71","tid":1112971,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"唔止佢 好撚多歌手都係咁<br />\n好撚憎"}]}